.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12973092/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Vascular+and+nonvascular+complications+of+liver+transplants%3A+sonographic+evaluation+and+correlation+with+other+imaging+modalities+and+findings+at+surgery+and+pathology&amp;author=SM+Friedewald&amp;author=EP+Molmenti&amp;author=MR+DeJong&amp;author=UM+Hamper&amp;publication_year=2003&amp;journal=Ultrasound+Q&amp;pages=71-85&amp;doi=10.1097%2F00013644-200306000-00003&amp;pmid=12973092">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">4.</div><div id="r4" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Ito K, Siegelman ES, Stolpen AH, Mitchell DG MR imaging of complications after liver transplantation. <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em> 2000;175(4): 1145–1149.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/ajr.175.4.1751145">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11000180/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=MR+imaging+of+complications+after+liver+transplantation&amp;author=K+Ito&amp;author=ES+Siegelman&amp;author=AH+Stolpen&amp;author=DG+Mitchell&amp;publication_year=2000&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=1145-1149&amp;doi=10.2214%2Fajr.175.4.1751145&amp;pmid=11000180">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">5.</div><div id="r5" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Nghiem HV Imaging of hepatic transplantation. <em>Radiol Clin North Am</em> 1998;36(2):429–443.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/S0033-8389(05)70033-6">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9520993/"